claim: Hayden Panettiere starred as Sheryl Yoast in Remember the Titans.
premise_source_doc_sentence: She began her acting career by playing Sarah Roberts on One Life to Live  (  1994 -- 97  )  , and Lizzie Spaulding on Guiding Light  (  1996 -- 2000  )  , before starring at age 10 as Sheryl Yoast in the Disney feature film Remember the Titans .
